## Hardware Connections

Motor Driver (TB6612FNG)

PWMA → Arduino Pin 5  
PWMB → Arduino Pin 6  
AIN1 → Arduino Pin 3  
AIN2 → Arduino Pin 4  
BIN1 → Arduino Pin 7  
BIN2 → Arduino Pin 8  

Sensor Array → A0–A7
Emitter Pin → Digital 2


